title: r/Choosingbeggars I Got An Iphone 11 For X-Mas... I HATE MY FAMILY!
description: r/Choosingbeggars It's January, which means Christmases all over the worlds have been ruined by mean, evil parents who refused to buy their parents an Xbox, and a PS5, and the newest iPhone.
